description.p:
Yet another embodiment of the present invention is a process for preparing the above polymer, comprising reacting a diacid or a diester of formula (X):

wherein Y is a straight chain or branched aliphatic or olefinic or aromatic group having up to 20 carbon atoms and up to 8 double bonds, preferably having up to 10 carbons atoms and up to 2 double bonds, and R is a hydrogen atom or an alkyl group;

with a diamine of formula (XI):

wherein p is an integer in the range of from 2 to 10; and m is an integer in the range of from 1 to 10;

to form a poly(aminoamide) and reacting said poly(aminoamide) with at least one compound selected from the group consisting of alkylating agents, an acylating agents, and an alkyl isocyanates, wherein said alkylating agents, acylating agents, and alkyl isocyanates comprise a straight chain or branched aliphatic or olefinic group having up to 22 carbon atoms, up to 4 double bonds, and an amine-reactive functional group.

Another aspect of the present invention is directed to a process for preparing the water soluble polymers of the present invention. This process comprises (a) reacting a diacid or a diester of formula (X):

wherein Y is a straight chain or branched aliphatic or olefinic or aromatic group having up to 20 carbon atoms and up to 8 double bonds, preferably having up to 10 carbons and 2 double bonds, and R is a hydrogen atom or an alkyl group;

with a diamine of formula (XI):

wherein p is an integer in the range of from 2 to 10; and m is an integer in the range of from 1 to 10;

to form a poly(aminoamide), and step (b) reacting said poly(aminoamide) with at least one compound selected from the group consisting of alkylating agents, an acylating agents, and an alkyl isocyanates, wherein said alkylating agents, acylating agents, and alkyl isocyanates comprise a straight chain or branched aliphatic or olefinic group having up to 22 carbon atoms, up to 4 double bonds, and an amine-reactive functional group.

claim.claim-text:
Eine Zusammensetzung umfassend das Polymer gemäß Anspruch 1 und wenigstens eine zusätzliche Verbindung, wobei die betreffende wenigstens eine zusätzliche Verbindung ausgewählt wird aus der Gruppe bestehend aus
(a) Schadstoffschutzmitteln für Ablagerungen von Zellstoffharz und klebrigen Verunreinigungen;
(b) Ablagerungsschutzmitteln für Papierherstellungsausrüstungen;
(c) Flockungsmitteln für die Wasserbehandlung;
(d) Koagulanzien für die Wasserbehandlung;
(e) Entwässerungshilfsmitteln zur Papierherstellung;
(f) Retentionshilfsmitteln für die Papierherstellung;
(g) Schlichtemitteln für Papiererzeugnisse;
(h) Klebstoffen;
(i) Kreppklebstoffen;
(j) Weichmachern zur Optimierung von Harzeigenschaften
(k) Modifizierungsmitteln zur Optimierung von Harzeigenschaften;
(l) Reinigungsmitteln; und
(m) Lösehilfsmitteln.

A composition comprising the polymer of claim 1 and at least one additional compound, wherein said at least one additional compound is selected from the group consisting of
(a) contaminant control agents for pitch and stickies deposits;
(b) deposition control agents for papermaking process equipment;
(c) flocculants for water treatment;
(d) coagulants for water treatment;
(e) drainage aids for papermaking;
(f) retention aids for papermaking;
(g) sizing agent for paper products;
(h) adhesives;
(i) creping adhesives;
(j) plasticizers for optimizing resin properties;
(k) modifiers for optimizing resin properties;
(l) cleaning aids; and
(m) release aids.

Composition comprenant le polymère selon la revendication 1 et au moins un composé supplémentaire, dans lequel ledit au moins un composé supplémentaire est choisi dans le groupe constitué par
(a) les agents limitant les contaminants pour les dépôts de poix et de matières collantes ;
(b) les agents limitant les dépôts pour un matériel de procédé de fabrication du papier ;
(c) des floculants pour le traitement de l'eau ;
(d) des coagulants pour le traitement de l'eau ;
(e) des adjuvants d'égouttage pour la fabrication du papier ;
(f) des adjuvants de rétention pour la fabrication du papier ;
(g) un agent d'encollage pour les produits en papier ;
(h) des adhésifs ;
(i) des adhésifs de crêpage ;
(j) des plastifiants pour optimiser les propriétés d'une résine ;
(k) des agents de modification pour optimiser les propriétés d'une résine ;
(l) des adjuvants de nettoyage ; et
(m) des adjuvants de démoulage.
